description:
**Job Description:**

KIA of Riverdale is looking for a Service BDC Manager to join our team.

**Job Requirements:**

· Previous Sales experience;

· Competitive and self-motivated attitude that thrives on goals;

· Team player with positive energy and an eagerness to improve;

· Previous management experience preferred;

· Automotive industry experience preferred;

· Ready to waste no time on learning new product in’s and out’s, eager to improve;

· Ability to manage a high volume of inbound and outbound sales and service call volume, internet leads and call lists;

· Outgoing personality, ability to influence customers to schedule appointments;

· Strong computer knowledge;

· Phenomenal communication skills with customers and team members;

· Experience in previous automotive dealerships, with 5 years’ experience specifically with BDC/internet;

·Extremely customer service oriented;

·Must have strong computer skills;

· Enthusiastic personality;

· Must be Dependable and Reliable.

**Responsibilities:**

· Ensures all internet leads are followed up with until competition of sale;

· Exhibit ethical behavior, provide the highest degree of customer satisfaction, and be honest in all aspects of dealing with customers;

· Answer customer inquiries and calls when necessary;

· Follows up with aged sales leads;

· Manage and track all leads;

· Manage all incoming and outgoing phone calls and emails;

· Maintain daily, weekly, and monthly sales forecasts;

· Work closely with executive and department managers to develop appointment-setting strategies;

· Handle our customer contacts through CRM, service, follow-up, and lead generation;

· Schedule sales/service appointments and reschedule no-show customers.

· Provide training and ongoing support to the business development representatives to help the team understand and achieve the dealership’s goals;

· Learn to overcome objections and thrive within sales situations;

· Answer customer internet inquiries by both email and phone;

· Manage the day-to-day business of the business development center;

· Achieve the sales and customer satisfaction objectives set by management.

**Benefits:**  
We offer health, dental, vision, life insurance, paid vacation time along with great pay!

Job Type: Full-time

Pay: $85,000.00 - $150,000.00 per year

Benefits:

* 401(k)
* 401(k) matching
* Dental insurance
* Health insurance
* Life insurance
* Paid time off
* Vision insurance

Schedule:

* 8 hour shift
* Monday to Friday

Education:

* High school or equivalent (Required)

Experience:

* Customer service: 1 year (Required)
* BDC Manager: 1 year (Required)
* Automotive Dealership: 1 year (Required)
* Automotive service: 1 year (Required)

License/Certification:

* Driver's License (Required)

Ability to Relocate:

* Riverdale, NJ 07457: Relocate before starting work (Required)

Work Location: In person
